name: Witch Cottage
description:
Holda is the main antagonist of the 2020 dark fantasy horror film Gretel and Hansel directed by Oz Perkins
Holda takes the form of an elderly woman to lure abandoned children into her house (Witch Cottage) with enchanted body parts disguised as food, after which she kills and eats them to empower her witchcraft.
The Witch Cottage, also known as "Holda's House", is a dark wooden cottage home to the horrid witch Holda.

She eats children in this place, and after that, she says

"Well, another one bites the dust."
